WEBVTT

00:13:00.000 --> 00:13:03.256
to approach these patients
with dignity and respect,

00:13:03.280 --> 00:13:05.200
just like we expect.

00:13:06.640 --> 00:13:09.056
I remember being
in my 11th grade literature class,

00:13:09.080 --> 00:13:11.256
with one of my favorite
teachers, Mr. McClain,

00:13:11.280 --> 00:13:14.896
and he shared this quote by Heraclitus
that sticks with me to this day.

00:13:14.920 --> 00:13:16.576
Y'all may have even heard it.

00:13:16.600 --> 00:13:20.600
It's, "The only thing that is constant
is that things will change."

00:13:22.600 --> 00:13:23.800
Familiar, right?

00:13:24.640 --> 00:13:27.776
Every single one of us
face changes in our lives,

00:13:27.800 --> 00:13:30.136
and often when we're faced
with these changes,